      <listitem>
        <para>
          You can access to this command from the
          image menubar through
          <menuchoice><guimenu><accel>F</accel>ile</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open <accel>R</accel>ecent</guimenuitem></menuchoice>,
        </para>
